attributes.description: Juicy sausages. Creamy mash. Onion marmalade? Not your regular trio, we know. It’s onion marmalade that gives your gravy a rich tang, bringing this British comfort classic to life. Vibrant peas and oven-roasted carrots make it bursting with goodness too!
